NOT TO MENTION BARD SKIN INC. ;o

{{champion:96}} 
This champion is the most adorable champion in the game. Hands down. It's like having your adorable little digital puppy that you train and wreck havoc with late game. Especially if you spam ctrl 1 taunt throughout the whole game. Charge! :P 

On a sidenote though, I'm really disappointed with the current state of this champion and the condition of the last two patches he's been in. Really Riot, the reason he was capable of doing so well to begin with was because Triforce gave him HP, you received HP in your masteries, he actually did 'decent' mixed damage when he pressed his W, and he had been slightly more mobile than he currently is with the 5 additional movespeed, slightly tankier stats and a skill that didn't lock him down. From a diehard Kog main, please take this into consideration if you see it. He needs stat buffs in addition to an AD buff. Just my opinion. He's in an awful place right now. #SaveTheVoidPuppy

{{champion:432}} 
Simply because he has a cool minigame that changes the game that only helps him instead of forcing him into a specific playstyle. The experience of Bard is unlike any other champion.
Then you add on that he is the most unique character in the game. No one comes near how unique he is and how cool is Lore is. Not to mention he is technically the most powerful being currently in the game, with only Kindred coming near him.

{{champion:432}} 
