pre rework {{champion:82}}

{{champion:35}} 
"Look behind you!"

I just love how you can set up mindgames, trick your enemies and how flexible you can build this guy. He's one of the few champs who can actually utilize a huge chunk of the available items and he feels quite balanced since he has obvious weaknesses and counterplay, but still has a chance to play around this. :)
